Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:04.73,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Let's bring on our next presenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,200)}Original subs: royaltree1204\NAdditional subs: oolong\NUpdates and QC: GakiDave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.29,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Who's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:15.09,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's Daikichi Hakata!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:19.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Daikichi, the teacher who looks good in a V-neck sweater.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to dress up like a person on a supermarket ad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anyone heard of the term, "homing instinct"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooya-san, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's people who can get home even though they're drunk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.69,0:00:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, they somehow are able to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's essentially what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that Ooya-san would give the correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many animals who have it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you say, "homing instinct," then pigeons may be the most famous for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:55.45,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:00:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The most famous would be the messenger pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that even if they're 1,000km away, they're able to figure out their way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,200)}T/N: 1,000km = 621.3 miles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,1,000km is approximately the distance from Tokyo to Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that distance is pretty easy for them to find their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you hear this, you think, "pigeons are amazing".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mad respect for pigeons
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I have brought this kind of theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:26.43,Hamada,,0,0,0,,The theory that humans have a better homing instinct than pigeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.95,0:01:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's amazing for a pigeon to return home to Tokyo from Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, if you were abandoned in Hokkaido, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,200)}T/N: Hokkaido is the northernmost island in Japan and known for the harsh cold temperatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:38.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd get back home one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Futo-san, how about you, if you were abandoned in Okinawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,200)}T/N: Okinawa is the southernmost island in Japan and known for the warm tropical weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd relax and take my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:50.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We're talking about going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:52.67,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Though it depends on the season.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:59.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We verify if humans have a better homing instinct than pigeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:05.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tonight we enlist the help of a pigeon coop in Saitama prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:11.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Roughly 500km from Tohoku's mountainous region...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:17.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...we hold an exhibition race.  \NWho will get home faster: human or pigeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:27.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,190)}(Question: Can pigeons win against humans?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My first thought is that the pigeons will come out on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:24.19,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:30.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so the person they choose to go against the pigeons is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:32.77,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why from here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,960)}Yasuda Dai Circus\NKuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the awful staff again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff:  You'll know when you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something Inoki Kanji would say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,200)}T/N: Inoki Kanji (aka Antonio Inoki) had a famous saying about how even if you wonder about what will happen if you go down a certain path, you'll know when you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:00.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that said, we put on the eyemask...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:05.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and begin our journey to the starting line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't predict anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Were you able to predict things before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, definitely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:19.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With this, the car travels down the freeway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:25.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...roughly eight hours to the starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:30.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,7:00 the next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:34.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We arrive at a mountain in the Tohoku region.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff:  Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that kind of long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:52.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time we start from...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:55.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Iwate Prefecture, Shimoheigun, Iwaizumi town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:04:00.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No station, and practically no roads nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An area with nothing in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:08.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, the temperature today is -3C.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold!  So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really cold, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:19.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In shorts and short-sleeves...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:22.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Kuro-chan is perhaps underdressed for Iwate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is absolutely in the minuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Both participants take their starting positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:36.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To make things fair we confiscate his phone and wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:42.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As the pigeons aren't privy to knowing where they are, we start without either one knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:46.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As a result, will the human win?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:50.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or will the pigeons?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.97,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Scary...he doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:09.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,(Rule: The pigeon that returns earliest out of the ten pigeons will be their time.)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:18.97,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:21.88,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You're not going to\Ntell him it started?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get the meaning of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?  Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:35.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan doesn't realize the race has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.99,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:42.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time there are others besides Kuro-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I just followed my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had them buy my ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:57.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An old man who has never ridden on the train by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:07.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even an 8-year old is going on their first errand alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,All start roughly at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:15.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes after the pigeons took flight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:20.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Kuro-chan shows no signs of starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do I stand here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:31.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It seems the frequent blindfolding has \Ntrained him not to remove the eyemask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:35.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He doesn't remove the eyemask until he's instructed to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:40.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is very disciplined in that sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:45.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seriously, one hour later...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I have to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to leak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.29,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,We did start from\Nthe bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I don't understand.  What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it start?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take off my eyemask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,HELLO?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take off the eyemask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ok, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.29,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Even if he asks this \None question, they \Ncan't answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:38.85,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"Take the camera and go to the next location."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Page 1?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Saitama Prefecture, Koshigaya"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I supposed to go here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is different than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...really, what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:25.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As a result, who will reach the goal first?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:45.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One hour since the start of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:48.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The current situation is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently heading towards Route 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:58.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To get the help of local people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...the old man heads to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:09.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mother told him, "if you're in trouble, ask someone for help."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:14.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ringo-kun, for the time being, looks for a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:24.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Kuro-chan, who started an hour later than the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With no knowledge of what is going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:36.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...he walks into the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate I have to go this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,An Iwate Prefecture car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:56.55,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He looked at the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is this Iwate prefecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:03.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan managed to get a significant hint...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:05.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...from the plates of the passing car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have talked to that car just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:16.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After walking another ten minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like a workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's someone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1065,906)}Eh? Are you Kuro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1160,910)}Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a second to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, can I get you in the shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me where I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... Iwaizumi town in Iwate prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}Iwate prefecture?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohoku's Iwate prefecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}Yes, Tohoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, from here I have to go to Koshigaya in Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get to Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}Saitama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There really isn't much in the way of public transportation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:14.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is able to find his current location, but there are no stations around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:17.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There aren't any freeways around either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:20.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Quite a hopeless situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a car here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be possible for you to take me somewhere by car?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For now, with the generosity of a local...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:34.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...he is able to get to the nearest station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.99,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are in a tough place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Other shows aren't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They're messed in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:51.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Ringo-kun was looking for a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:01.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not able to find anyone and tired from walking, he sits down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:07.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As for the old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind giving me a ride to the station on the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Komoto station ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:19.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hitchhiking for the first time in his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:23.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...he is the first to arrive at a station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:28.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And as for the pigeons?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:38.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are likely making good progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:38.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,200)}(※ - Stock footage)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:38.12,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Right, filming them\Nwas impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Two hours since the start of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:48.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As the old man waits outside by the bus stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:56.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Kuro-chan also arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So from here I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,From here, go to Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the fastest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then from Miyako go to Morioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then from Morioka...you can get there by bullet train or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Based on the suggestion we would aim for Morioka, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:23.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Kuro-chan currently has no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:25.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now you are at this place called Omoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be the fastest way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:40.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There is a two-hour wait for the next train.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But with no money, there is also no train.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While this is going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1200,840)}Kuro-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:56.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Locals who recognize Kuro-chan come to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you don't have enough for the train fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}I have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They left him with an eyemask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not "ah...", this isn't normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how I'm dressed.  Isn't this strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how long would it take by car?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}From here to Miyako, probably about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,About an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were to Miyako, the three of us could ride together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}We can take you as far as Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We are heading to the Miyako site anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:34.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He gets a ride to Miyako station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:45.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Ringo-kun discovers a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda on this errand by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,(Shows the paper) Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}That's Saitama prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:03.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ringo-kun gets a ride to the station from a kind stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.19,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So many nice people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Three hours since the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,810)}Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He accepts a bento from a local shopping street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:22.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His first meal of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard filming, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:36.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With zero funds, Kuro-chan gets this suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you get get home with 5,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Offer to have your picture taken at my job site.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, 1,000 yen per shot with five people is 5,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you kind of give me a ride there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A dangerous schemer appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Kuroda Kanbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,200)}T/N: Kuroda Kanbei was a feudal lord known for his quick wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:04.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that said, they stop at their job site...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:11.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...annd raise funds with pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pose, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kuro-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for accepting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use this money wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:29.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He gets 6,000 yen total.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With everyone's strength I'm able to return home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're getting on the bus at Miyako station...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...to Morioka will be 2,030 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,2,030 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,From Morioka, take the bullet train for 8,230 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,8,230 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:55.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their research indicated that to get to Saitama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:58.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...it would require 10,260 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:01.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Currently short by 4,260 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:06.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the always-happy Kuro-chan!  Wah-wah-wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiji-san, thank you so much for the 2,260 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:23.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Recording individual messages to the local townsfolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:28.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With this, the goal of 10,260 yen has been reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you'll get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, looks like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I get back, I'm not sure if it's finished or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really not sure what I'm actually participating in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Kuro-chan has no knowledge of what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:52.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tonight's challenge is Humans vs Homing Pigeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:57.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Surely the pigeons are having a nice flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:02.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Currently among them, the old man is in last place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:11.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After failing to get on the bus, he now aims to get to Morioka by hitchhiking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, which way are you heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...Morioka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He gets a car heading to Morioka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...suddenly coming up from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:34.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Ringo-kun arrived at Miyako Station before Kuro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:40.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just as he was directed: onto the bus to Morioka station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:46.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, perhaps exhausted from his first trip alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...he falls fast asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:56.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Kuro-chan, who got a ride to Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this ok with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:04.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...got a ride with a family going to Morioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you laugh there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:15.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With this, all three are aiming for Morioka at roughly the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:21.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the first to arrive at Morioka station is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:24.43,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:29.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What?! It's Kuro-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to get the money collected earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:35.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and get on a bullet train.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The goal is close at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:42.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But, as one would expect, a situation arises!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:47.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan is the first to arrive at Morioka station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:51.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But a situation has arisen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:20:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd like to go to Koshigaya in Saitama prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}To Koshigaya would be a total of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}...a total of 13,170 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,13,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,13,000 yen, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the cheapest price?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:18.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It looks like the researched price was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, oh no, oh no, oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The calculations were completely off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:29.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your marriage Manabe! Wah wah wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:40.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He sells wedding congratulation messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:45.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And in just five minutes, he's raised 6,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:49.93,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You can make it with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:54.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With this, he acquires a bullet train ticket and taxi fare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a crazy journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:03.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From the funds, a bullet train ride and a regular train ride...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:07.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...for two and a half hours ends in Saitama's Kasukabe station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Made it to Kasukabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:18.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After that, get to the goal destination in a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, I really made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:27.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is it!  This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Eleven hours and twenty seven minutes since the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:40.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Kuro-chan reaches the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is here ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: You reached an admirable goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't do something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: This is the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end? It's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(395,1003,848,1060)}Staff: But Kuro-chan...you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: But Kuro-chan...you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:12.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.  Five hours earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, they're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:26.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The pigeons came in first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:28.25,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Faster than in a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.09,0:22:30.42,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.42,0:22:34.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Also, 30 minutes before Kuro-chan arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:38.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...the old man arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:45.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Also, Ringo-kun, who arrived 15 minutes before Kuro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,820)}Staff: You lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "yes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost to who? I didn't lose to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:22:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't up against anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Pigeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pigeons?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:12.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan's face looks like he's been shot by a peashooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:15.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here at last we explain the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: By the way, this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(156,1000,780,1080)}Staff: We released ten pigeons...and two came back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: We released ten pigeons...and two came back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other eight?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the bigger question?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:32.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that said, pigeons will return faster from Tohoku than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, most never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:41.15,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, unfortunately, humans lost, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...wasn't that clever of Kuro-chan to get back the way he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:51.57,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Clever or maybe devilish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,His method seemed very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.29,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And there's also...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:59.65,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...they didn't show even one heartwarming moment by Ringo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.65,0:24:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there were a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:03.77,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Would you just gloss that over?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.99,0:24:06.11,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,An 8-year-old who does his very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.11,0:24:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't show the kid's uneasiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should change that background music. I feel sorry for the other show.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,200)}T/N: The background music they used for Ringo-kun comes from the show, "My First Errand", a show about young kids running their first errand all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.78,0:24:15.98,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Like the mother's tears and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.98,0:24:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan can make that much money...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.11,0:24:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...how much could Matsumoto-san make?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.91,0:24:24.49,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I personally can't use Kuro-chan's sort of simple methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.49,0:24:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, his worth...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.69,0:24:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If Matsumoto-san were doing photos on the spot like that, he could probably get 10,000 yen per!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.69,0:24:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,200)}T/N: 10,000yen was approximately worth $82.61USD at the time this episode aired.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.75,0:24:31.75,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.49,0:24:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.75,0:24:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how much we can earn!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go try to see how much you can earn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.80,0:24:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then please come back by helicopter or something.

